overview: The all-time bestseller of the Jocks series! Bob Bishop, of Colt and Brentwood fame, headlines this star-studded cast with Ed Wiley, Rod Mitchell, Will Seagers, and six other sexual athletes, including Scott O'Hara - "the biggest cock in San Francisco" - and blond Brian Hawks. Winner "Best Video" of 1984. Includes the short films: "Ramcharger," "Tutor," "The Bigger They Are," "Hard Pressed," and a solo by Matt Hollis.
title: Ramcharger
